flowchart TD
  U[User] --> UI[Next.js UI\nChatInterface]
  UI -->|toggle agentMode| LS[(localStorage\nmcs_agent_mode_v1)]
  UI -->|toggle provider/mode| CT[ComputeToggle]
  CT --> RTMODE[/api/runtime/mode\nGET/POST/]
  CT --> BRTSTATE[/api/backend/v1/runtime/state\n(proxy/stub)/]
  CT --> SRVLATEST[/api/servers/latest/]
  SRVLATEST --> REG[(data/server-registry.json)]
  RTMODE --> MODE[(data/runtime-mode.json)]
  RTMODE --> EVTS[(data/runtime-events.jsonl)]
  RTMODE -->|sync| CPURTMODE[CPU FastAPI\n/v1/runtime/mode]

  UI -->|POST agentMode=0| LLM[/api/llm-chat/]
  UI -->|POST agentMode=1| AG[/api/agent-chat/]

  LLM --> SOS1{SOS check}
  SOS1 -->|trigger| OUTSOS1[response+sos metadata]
  SOS1 -->|no| SAFE1{Safety block?}
  SAFE1 -->|block| OUTBLK1[blocked response]
  SAFE1 -->|ok| ROUTE1{Routing\nruntime-mode.json\n+ server-registry.json}
  ROUTE1 -->|gpu| GPUCHAT[GPU OpenAI-like\n/v1/chat/completions]
  ROUTE1 -->|cpu| CPUCHAT[CPU FastAPI\n/v1/chat/completions]
  GPUCHAT -->|fail| FALL1{Fallback}
  FALL1 -->|GEMINI key| GEM1[GeminiService\n(generateFromConfig)]
  FALL1 -->|else| CPUCHAT
  CPUCHAT --> OUTLLM[LLM response + metadata\npersist chat + metrics]
  GEM1 --> OUTLLM
  OUTLLM --> UI

  AG --> SOS2{SOS check}
  SOS2 -->|trigger| OUTSOS2[response+metadata]
  SOS2 -->|no| SAFE2{Safety block?}
  SAFE2 -->|block| OUTBLK2[blocked response]
  SAFE2 -->|ok| ROUTE2{Routing\nruntime-mode.json\n+ server-registry.json}
  ROUTE2 -->|gpu| OAIGPU[runLocalAgent\n-> GPU /v1/chat/completions\n(JSON actions)]
  ROUTE2 -->|cpu| OAICPU[runLocalAgent\n-> CPU /v1/chat/completions\n(JSON actions)]
  OAIGPU -->|fail| AGFALL{Fallback}
  AGFALL -->|has key| GEM2[GeminiService\n(generateAgent + tools)]
  AGFALL -->|no key| OAICPU
  GEM2 -->|tool calls| MCP[/api/mcp/call/]
  MCP --> WEB[web.search\n(DDG/Google CSE)]
  MCP --> YT[youtube.*]
  GEM2 --> OUTAG[AgentResponse\nresponse+actions+metadata\npersist + metrics]
  OAIGPU --> OUTAG
  OAICPU --> OUTAG
  OUTAG --> UI
  UI -->|render planned messages\n(special embeds/music/nav)| UI
  UI -->|execute speak action| TTS[/api/text-to-speech-stream\nfallback /api/text-to-speech/]